divs: Sighting DetailsI and my son walked outside to help the rest of our family to bring in stuff from the store around 9:15 pm and we seen two glowing objects rising from the west side of Albuquerque in a southern path they both had a white disk or round upper parts and the lower halfs seem to be on fire. One took off strait up towards the stars and one slowly went up we could see it getting farther away it was moving very fast till we colud not see it any more. Here on that night the moon was full so it lit up the night sky very well we got some still photos on are phones
Summary: Two glowing white disks with what appeared to be fire like glow one shot strait up one kinda floated up in western sky very odd witnessed by 3 adults 4 kids
